 with Scallion Corn Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-3-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-3-scaled.jpg 1737w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-3-728x922.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-3-768x973.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-3-1213x1536.jpg 1213w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-3-1617x2048.jpg 1617w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-3-150x190.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1737px) 100vw, 1737px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI use our grill every single day in the summer… sometimes twice a day. My kids actually want to eat vegetables when they are grilled, everyone enjoys chicken, salmon and steak – the options are endless. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled buffalo chicken with corn salad\" width=\"1765\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/grilled-buffalo-chicken-thighs/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Grilled Buffalo Chicken with Scallion Corn Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-4-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-4-scaled.jpg 1765w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-4-728x907.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-4-768x957.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-4-1232x1536.jpg 1232w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-4-1643x2048.jpg 1643w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-4-150x187.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1765px) 100vw, 1765px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSo! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis is one of our favorite ways to make buffalo chicken right now. It’s similar to how I make the \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/06/grilled-bbq-chicken-sandwiches/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBBQ chicken sandwiches that I just shared\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e. And it’s freaking delicious!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI marinate the chicken in some buffalo wing sauce. I grill it and then right before it’s finished, cover with a slice of sharp cheddar cheese.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt gets all melty and fantastic and is incredible. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-5-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled buffalo chicken with corn salad\" width=\"1784\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/grilled-buffalo-chicken-thighs/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Grilled Buffalo Chicken with Scallion Corn Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-5-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-5-scaled.jpg 1784w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-5-728x898.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-5-768x947.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-5-1246x1536.jpg 1246w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-5-1661x2048.jpg 1661w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-5-150x185.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1784px) 100vw, 1784px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThen! The best part.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe top gets covered with a grilled corn and scallion salad. Complete with lots of fresh lime juice, chives and cilantro. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWe eat a version of this corn salad every summer. It’s ridiculously simple and so easy to make. I throw the corn right on the grill with the chicken. But the best part is that you don’t even have to cook the corn.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-99972\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled buffalo chicken with corn salad\" width=\"1838\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/grilled-buffalo-chicken-thighs/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Grilled Buffalo Chicken with Scallion Corn Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-8-scaled.jpg 1838w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-8-728x871.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-8-768x919.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-8-1284x1536.jpg 1284w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-8-1711x2048.jpg 1711w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-8-150x179.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1838px) 100vw, 1838px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHave you ever tried it fresh right off the cob? It’s so crisp, crunchy and sweet. We adore it. That means that technically, this can be a fresh corn or a grilled corn salad. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAdd your favorite herbs. Some green onions.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYou can even throw in some feta or cotija cheese if you wish!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-10-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled buffalo chicken with corn salad\" width=\"1871\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/grilled-buffalo-chicken-thighs/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Grilled Buffalo Chicken with Scallion Corn Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-10-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-10-scaled.jpg 1871w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-10-728x856.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-10-768x903.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-10-1306x1536.jpg 1306w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-10-1741x2048.jpg 1741w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-10-150x176.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1871px) 100vw, 1871px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLots of lime juice, salt and pepper – you’re golden. It’s the best side that comes together in mere minutes. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-11-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled buffalo chicken with corn salad\" width=\"1723\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/grilled-buffalo-chicken-thighs/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Grilled Buffalo Chicken with Scallion Corn Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-11-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-11-scaled.jpg 1723w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-11-728x930.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-11-768x981.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-11-1203x1536.jpg 1203w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-11-1604x2048.jpg 1604w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-11-150x192.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1723px) 100vw, 1723px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI love putting the corn salad right on top of the chicken too. Just like a salsa.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt tastes so special and fancy but it’s really very easy!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled buffalo chicken with corn salad\" width=\"1746\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/grilled-buffalo-chicken-thighs/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Grilled Buffalo Chicken with Scallion Corn Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-scaled.jpg 1746w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-728x917.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-768x968.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-1219x1536.jpg 1219w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-1625x2048.jpg 1625w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-150x189.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1746px) 100vw, 1746px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eGrilled Buffalo Chicken with Scallion Corn Salad\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-99989\" data-recipe-id=\"99989\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-14-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eGrilled Buffalo Chicken with Scallion Corn Salad\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"99989\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e40\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThese grilled buffalo chicken thighs are so easy and delicious! Covered in cheddar cheese and served with a grilled corn scallion salad, this meal is the epitome of summer. Light, refreshing, satisfying and simple!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"recipe-99989-ingredients\" data-recipe=\"99989\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 ½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epounds\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eboneless, skinless chicken thighs\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ebuffalo wing sauce,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efrank’s red hot wing sauce is our favorite\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e6\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eto 8\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eears of corn\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/green-onions-5-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-78873596?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003escallions,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ethinly sliced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¼\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/organic-chives-0-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-79495118?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echopped chives\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¼\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/cilantro-bunch-each/-/A-15006468?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003echopped fresh cilantro\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/lime-each/-/A-15026731?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003elimes,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efreshly juiced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4 to 6\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eslices\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/tillamook-sharp-cheddar-cheese-loaf-8oz/-/A-52252287?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003esharp cheddar cheese,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eor however many thighs you have\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"recipe-99989-instructions\" data-recipe=\"99989\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99989-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eSeason the chicken all over with salt and pepper. Place it in a dish, bowl or resealable bag and cover it with ⅔ cup of the buffalo wing sauce. Place it in the fridge (cover if in a dish/bowl). Marinate for at least 30 minutes and even overnight.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99989-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePreheat your grill to the highest setting and remove the chicken from the fridge.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99989-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eOnce the grill is hot, place the corn directly on the grates and grill for 2 to 3 minutes before rotating. Repeat this until the corn has been grilled all around and has a few char marks. Remove the corn from the grill and let it cool until it can be handled comfortably.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99989-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlace the chicken directly on the grill and let the excess marinade drip off bag into the bowl/bag. Grill for 6 minutes. Flip, and grill for 6 minutes more, or until the internal temperature reaches 165 degrees F.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99989-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile the chicken is grilling, cut the corn from the cob. Add in the scallions, chives, cilantro and lime juice. Add a pinch of salt and pepper and toss.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99989-step-0-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eRight before the chicken is done, cover each piece with a slice of cheddar. Close the lid and let the cheese melt for 1 minute or so. Remove the chicken from the grill. Drizzle it all with the remaining wing sauce.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99989-step-0-6\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eServe the chicken with the corn salad!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMain Course\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-13-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"grilled buffalo chicken with corn salad\" width=\"1898\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/grilled-buffalo-chicken-thighs/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Grilled Buffalo Chicken with Scallion Corn Salad.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-13-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-13-scaled.jpg 1898w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-13-728x844.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-13-768x890.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-13-1325x1536.jpg 1325w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-13-1767x2048.jpg 1767w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/buffalo-chicken-and-corn-salad-13-150x174.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1898px) 100vw, 1898px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSummer staple alert!\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\u003c/article\u003e \n\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
